I’m a product designer and developer focused on building clear, scalable apps. I use design tools, low-code platforms, and structured thinking to turn ideas into working products. I aim to create systems that are intuitive, flexible, and maintainable, with just enough spice to make them feel delightful to use.

Currently, I’m a Lead Product Experience Engineer at Heimstaden, where I work across design, development and user adoption to deliver excellent user experiences. On the side, I build and test new product ideas to keep learning, and to find opportunity with technology.
